metadata.name: Casual Smokebreak
metadata.description: Deep inside ourselves hidden and unknown even to us our true self awaits. Unless we are brave enough to peel off the many layers we place atop our weaknesses we will never get to experience us. Are we a reflection of our own inner journey or perhaps just a virtual representation of who we think we ought to be? It's up to each individual to decide which version of ourselves is revealed when nobody is watching.
